videos.heading: Unit 1: Differential Calculus
videos.description: What is Differential Calculus?, Successive differentiation: Leibnitz’s Rule,Taylor’s.

videos.heading: Unit 2: Multivariable Calculus (Differentiation)
videos.description: Functions of several variables, First and Higher order partial derivatives, Euler’s theorem.

videos.heading: Unit 4: Matrices
videos.description: Inverse of a matrix by Partitioning method, Rank of a matrix, Consistency of linear system.

videos.heading: Unit 5: First Order Ordinary Differential Equations
videos.description: Linear, Reducible to linear and Bernoulli’s differential equations, Exact differential equations.

videos.heading: Unit 6: Higher Order Ordinary Differential Equations
videos.description: Higher order ordinary linear differential equations with constant coefficients.

videos.description: What is Multivariable Calculus? Double integrals (Cartesian and Polar).

videos.description: What is Vector Calculus?Vector triple product, Product of four vectors.
